{"tid":2140481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈成績表] I.T發盈警 料虧損逾億","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T08:37:05.000Z","uid":33730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28d382f958af23d828a875eda7d0b44c4a3fc37e","tid":2140481,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"I.T發盈警 料虧損逾億<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】商人沈嘉偉旗下的I.T（999）截至2月底止過去12個月財政年度，勁蝕7.5億元。期後虧損未見收窄，公司昨日發盈警補充指，<span class=\"red\">預計截至今年5月底止3個月蝕最少1億元</span>，去年同期則賺3,400萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200805/XQDJTEMZ7D5JB3SXGT57POA6NI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200805%2FXQDJTEMZ7D5JB3SXGT57POA6NI%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeav3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=1daa0938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200805%2FXQDJTEMZ7D5JB3SXGT57POA6NI%2F&h=9f7ed4d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200805/XQDJTEMZ7D5JB3SXGT57POA6NI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0a27d2938fa1998af1b906c1d23e52c146f737","tid":2140481,"uid":96383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:50:01.000Z","msg":"有保就業回血劍"},{"pid":"bbeb40c11049f2a71dedbeb35f802ab9afc44fb5","tid":2140481,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21678ea7a0f7a13d2ced7f6d3907e362e160b853","tid":2140481,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"在上周公布的名單中，時裝零售商I.T.  （00999）  ，領取